text: Novoufimsk () is a rural locality (a village) in Maysky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 22 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 90 km from Iglino, 35 km from Maysky. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Novoufimsk
